				\begin{document}$${\text{Dry cell weight}} = \frac{{\left( {\text{weight after filtration}} \right) - ({\text{weight before filtration}})}}{\text{volume of filtration}}$$\end{document}Specific growth rate (μ) was calculated as follows:μ=lnX2-lnX1t2-t1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
